{"tid":1478863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818建議事項","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:31:52.000Z","uid":294989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1999719afc46aa47f41da1ac8bfb650fc4c83bd5","tid":1478863,"uid":294989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"1.需留意可疑人士<br />\n2.但無須捉鬼<br />\n3.如有內鬼煽動<br />\n4.請孤立佢<br />\n5.保持距離<br />\n6.男士們要保護自己合女性(防禦拉距離)<br />\n7.女士們可幫手影罪證(但留意自身安全)<br />\n818和理非 市民上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4c199b108e9578db7a114763f272d8a4364c81","tid":1478863,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因果由國 容港治己<br />\n黃台之瓜 何堪再摘<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f1376341088229c73be0b161717df2675161859","tid":1478863,"uid":294989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"721.805.811"},{"pid":"422096e5899571ecd68e22086644dc152725e343","tid":1478863,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9848fab8fbbf590e8b577f49ec5b981cf3f84895","tid":1478863,"uid":294989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"721.805.811"},{"pid":"43ae93890fd3c41c70baae6ad54e6980540664fa","tid":1478863,"uid":294989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"721.805.811"},{"pid":"55c462fce62291aa11f0e5503011b56b9bab2268","tid":1478863,"uid":294989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:31:52.000Z","msg":"721.805.811"}]}